author: Doreen Christensen
title: JetBlue offers cheap fall/winter airfares
text:
JetBlue offers cheap fall/winter airfares JetBlue is having a fall airfare sale. Doreen Christensen Contact Reporter Sun Sentinel 
JetBlue is offering fall and winter airfare deals starting at $49 each way. 
Book travel by Oct. 21 for Monday through Thursday and Saturday departures from Nov. 4 through Feb. 10. 
Fly one way from Fort Lauderdale to Charleston, S.C., for $49, Baltimore for $59 and to Philadelphia for $99. each way. West Palm Beach to Newark is $124. 
From Orlando, offers are $89 one way to Washington and $119 to New York. 
Blackout dates: Nov. 20-Dec. 1, Dec. 17-Jan. 4, Jan. 18, among others for select cities. 
Click here for the deal. The offer ends at 11:59 p.m. Wednesday.
